_comment: Query 5 Results Analysis: This query counted the number of distinct values for each politician-applicable property across all instances, presenting 1,000 results ordered by frequency. The highest-frequency properties include foaf:topic (33,514 distinct values), dbo:wikiPageExternalLink (29,086 values), and Spanish DBpedia succession properties (es:predecesor with 27,822 values, es:sucesor). The range extends from properties with tens of thousands of distinct values down to properties with only 1 distinct value. This analysis reveals the data richness and variety within the knowledge graph, showing which properties have the most diverse value sets and indicating the complexity and interconnectedness of the political domain in DBpedia.
